<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Hugh Hefner's widow, Crystal Hefner, is remembering her late husband on the third anniversary of his death.</p>

<p>The former Playmate took to Instagram on Sunday, September 27, and shared a loving tribute to the Playboy magazine founder, who passed away at his home, dubbed the Playboy Mansion, in Holmby Hills, California at the age of 91. </p>

<p>'Three years. It's hard to believe,' the 34-year-old began in the caption of a photo of the couple snuggled up next to each other.</p>

<p>'Thank you for always being my greatest ally, teaching me the definition of kindness, and making me feel extremely important and adored for ten years. I will be forever grateful.'</p>

<p>Heartfelt: Crystal Hefner, 34, shared a loving tribute to her late husband Hugh Hefner on the third anniversary of his death; they are pictured in October 2014</p>

<p>In another tribute, Hefner (born Crystal Harris) shared the same photo of the couple on her Instagram Stories that she headlined: 'Thinking of this legend today.'</p>

<p>The model, who was the Playboy Playmate of the Month in December 2009, was married to Hefner from December 31, 2012, until his death on September 27, 2017.</p>

<p>They wed when he was 86 and she was 26 .</p>

<p>The legendary publisher died from sepsis that was brought on by a E. coli infection. Sepsis is an inflammatory immune response that arises when the body's response to infection causes injury to its tissues and organs.</p>

<p>Tribute: The former Playboy Playmate thanked her late husband for their time together in her Instagram post; the model was 26 and Hefner was 86 when they wed in December 2012</p>

<p>Crystal Hefner (born Cystal Harris) was the Playboy Playmate of the Month in December 2009; she is pictured in Mexico on September 3, 2020</p>

<p>Hefner's youngest son, Cooper, from his second marriage to model Kimberly Conrad, also took to Instagram to share a heartfelt tribute. </p>

<p>'We lost our father three years ago today. This will be an afternoon accompanied by Jack and Pepsi to celebrate him and our continued love,' the 28-year-old captioned a photo showing himself and brother Marston, 30, with their father when they were kids.</p>

<p>'We miss and love you, Dad.' </p>

<p>Hefner was married to Conrad from 1989 to 2010. </p>

<p>Memories: Hefner's youngest son, Cooper, from his second marriage to model Kimberly Conrad, also took to Instagram to share a heartfelt tribute</p>

<p>Hugh Hefner also left behind a daughter Christie, 67, and son David, 65, from his first marriage to Millie Williams from 1949 to 1959. </p>

<p>Just this past July, Crystal Hefner confirmed she's been dating Nathan Levi, 32, whom Page Six has previously identified as a spaceship engineer.  It's her first public relationship since Hugh's death.</p>

<p>The new couple were first linked when they were spotted packing on the PDAs at a resort in Mexico over the summer.    </p>

<p>New man in her life: Crystal Hefner is now dating Nathan Levi, 32, her first public relationship since the death of Hugh Hefner in September 2017</p>
